For building GtkHTML/Editor component with spell checking
you need pspell + some pspell module installed (aspell and/or
ispell modules)

They could be found here:

http://pspell.sourceforge.net/
http://aspell.sourceforge.net/ 

I do it like this:

	1) build and install pspell
	2) build and install aspell
	3) now do ./add_modules in pspell/modules directory and install it
	4) build and install gtkhtml

